24#include <sys/cdefs.h>
25__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_bar_gk20a.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
26
27#include "gf100.h"
28
29static const struct nvkm_bar_func
30gk20a_bar_func = {
31 .dtor = gf100_bar_dtor,
32 .oneinit = gf100_bar_oneinit,
33 .init = gf100_bar_init,
34 .umap = gf100_bar_umap,
35 .flush = g84_bar_flush,
36};
37
38int
39gk20a_bar_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_bar **pbar)
40{
41 int ret = gf100_bar_new_(&gk20a_bar_func, device, index, pbar);
42 if (ret == 0)
43 (*pbar)->iomap_uncached = true;
44 return ret;
45}
